# Expense Operating Amortisation Intangible Assets Infinite Life Amount

## identifier
de7505

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of amortisation charged to profit and loss in respect of intangible assets other than those with a finite life as determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.AmortisationIntangibleAssetsInfiniteLife.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
